column3: Bought this from Matt Christiano circa May 2024 for $2k, including an NOS playfield. Not known to work.
- Acquired for $800 from Jim Lewandowski of Riveriew IL on [[2024-12-19 Thursday]] - When purchased was in working shape with a couple of minor issues (sensors in top right)
Purchased June 2025 from a guy on FB Marketplace. It's a conversion of the 1941 Sky Blazer and the serial number is from there.
